  "body": "### Description\nCurrently in `BellatrixTransitionHelpers` when it is unable to verify that the terminal total difficulty conditions are met, it returns `SYNCING` without actually executing `executePayload` (or `newPayload` in the kiln spec).  This means the block may be optimistically imported without checking the block root which is not safe.\n\nWe should executePayload first and then check terminal total difficulty condition only if the block is VALID.",
